{
  "text": "An additional mechanism of Al tolerance in triticale was linked to plasma membrane lipid permeability to Al. When resistant and susceptible triticale lines expressed similar organic acid exudation under Al stress, the susceptible line expressed relatively greater root cell plasma membrane lipid permeability [CITATION_1] .",
